'''Siku''' i mpimo wa [[nkarhi]] lowu tekaka [[misava]] ku ndzuluka kan'we.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://scienceworld.wolfram.com/astronomy/Day.html |title=Day |author=Weisstein, Eric W. |year=2007 |accessdate=2011-05-31}}</ref> Siku ri nga thlela ri hlamusela mpimo wa nkarhi lowu tekaka [[dyambu]] ku sukela eka nhlekanhi leswaku ri pela, rithlela ri tsevuka ku fikela eka nhlekanhi wun'wana.<ref>
{{cite web |url=http://scienceworld.wolfram.com/astronomy/SolarDay.html |title=Solar Day |author=Weisstein, Eric W. |year=2007 |accessdate=2011-05-31}}</ref>

Hi lembe ra 1960, sekende yi hlamuseriwe hi kuya hi mandzulukele ya misava hi lembe ra 1900, naswona yi sungule ku tirhisiwa tani hi mpimo-ximfumo wa nkarhi. Hikokwalo siku ri sungule ku hlamuseriwa hi ku tirhisa mpimo wa sekende, naswona ri ringana na 86,400 wa ti sekende. Kasi hi 1967 sekende naswona hi ku landzelelana, siku swi hlamuseriwe hi mafambele ya ti [[Elektroni]] ta ti [[Athomu]].<ref name=Second>{{cite web |url=https://www.bipm.org/en/publications/si-brochure/second.html |title=Unit of time (second) |edition=8th |date=2014 |orig-year=2006 |website=SI Brochure |author=BIPM |authorlink=International Bureau of Weights and Measures |access-date=2019-08-26 |archive-date=2019-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190325064502/https://www.bipm.org/en/publications/si-brochure/second.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref> Hi ku angarhela, siku ri vumbiwa hi 86,400 wa ti sekende, laha ku nga havaka na sekende leyi engeteriwaka kumbe ku hungutiwa hi kuya hi mafambisele ya nkarhi wa misava (UTC), thlandla kwalano ku engetiwa kumbe ku hungutiwa awara e tindhzawini ta misava leti cincaka eka nhlayiso was kuvoakala ka dyambu.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://scienceworld.wolfram.com/astronomy/SolarDay.html |title=Solar Day |author=Weisstein, Eric W. |year=2007 |accessdate=2011-05-31}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://scienceworld.wolfram.com/astronomy/Day.html |title=Day |author=Weisstein, Eric W. |year=2007 |accessdate=2011-05-31}}</ref>

Siku rithlela ri hlamuseriwa hi mpimo wa ti [[awara]] ta makumembirhi-mune, ku suka exikarhi ka vusiku kuya eka byin'wana, laha [[vhiki]], [[nhweti]], kumbe [[lembe]] swi avanyisiwaka ha kona, hi ku landzelela mandzulukele ya misava.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://en.oxforddictionaries.com/definition/day|title=day – Definition of day in English by Oxford Dictionaries|author=|date=|website=Oxford Dictionaries – English}}</ref> Hambiswiritano, siku rihlamuseriwa hi ku hambana kuya hi mavulavulele ya vanhu, hi xikombiso vanhu vanga ha vula siku ro karhi ku hlamusela leswi endlekeke kusukela [[mixo]] ku ya eka [[ndzhengha]], ku mbe ku hambanisa exikarhi ka [[vusiku]] na [[nhlikanhi]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thefreedictionary.com/day|title=day|author=|date=|publisher=|via=The Free Dictionary}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.merriam-webster.com/dictionary/day|title=Definition of DAY|author=|date=|website=www.merriam-webster.com}}</ref><ref>Online Dictionary Definitions of "day".
